- Cuide-se.
- Eu vou.

977
00:51:50,204 --> 00:51:51,604
Feliz Natal.

978
00:52:02,708 --> 00:52:04,386
- Certo.
- Michael.

979
00:52:04,387 --> 00:52:05,804
- Kelly.
